<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="all-along">all along</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>[非正式用语] 一直；始终：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You’ve been very nice to me all along. 
你一直待我很好。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I know that all along. 
那件事我自始至终都知道。</p></div></div>